    "description": {
      "content": "The U.S. Geological Survey Water Services API provides real-time and historical surface-water, groundwater, and water-quality data for sites across the United States. Endpoints follow the WaterML / IV (instantaneous values), DV (daily values), and Site Service patterns.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: USGS Water Mission Area",
